[pagebreak] SPECIAL EDITION! EMPEROR AND HEIRS ASSASSINATED! A newspaper article on the assassination of Emperor Uriel Septim VII and his heirs. Elder Council Named as Regents!

[pagebreak]

mperor Uriel Septim VII is dead, at the age of 87, having ruled Tamriel for 65 years. He was killed by assassins unknown. At the same time, in separate locations, the late emperor's three sons and heirs (Crown Prince Geldall, 56; Prince Enman, 55; Prince Ebel, 53] were slain by other assassins. An investigation into the identity and motives of the assassins is under way, but the Elder Council, Imperial Guard, and Blades Guard have forbidden the publication of reports and rumors concerning the event until further notice. y ancient precedent, the Elder Council rules the empire until a new emperor is crowned. No direct heirs survive, and the council has proposed no list of candidates. Chancellor Ocato, Imperial Battlemage, speaking for the Elder Council, presented an appeal to the empire's citizens for calm, and asked that the people remember the Emperor, his sons, and the Elder Council in their prayers. mperor Uriel's early reign was marked by peace and prosperity. The Empress Caula Voria bore him three healthy sons, was a loving companion to the Emperor, and a great favorite of the people. However, the emperor and the empire suffered terribly during the Imperial Simulacrum (3E 389-399], when he was held captive in Oblivion while the usurper Jagar Tharn assumed his appearance and ruled in his stead. Emperor Uriel was finally rescued and restored and the impostor defeated by the agency of the sorceress Ria Silmane and her shadowy protege, but the affairs of the empire were in great disorder, and Empress Caula Voria, exhausted by her ordeal, withdrew from public life. he decades following the Restoration were once again peaceful and prosperous, but increasing political tensions among the petty states of northwest Tamriel finally erupted in the Wars of the Iliac Bays, resulting in the establishment of the modern borders of Daggerfall, Sentinel, Wayrest, and Orsinium, and culminating with the remarkable events associated with the Warp in the West. he latter years of the Emperor's reign have seen a flourishing of Imperial influence in the provinces, and with the fortunate resolution of the religious wars and the Vvardenfell Crisis, and with the wise and firm guidance of King Helseth and his mother, Queen Barenziah, an extension of high Imperial culture even into the more remote parts of Morrowind. he Emperor's murder, and the murder of his three sons, is a terrible crime, and a great tragedy for the Empire. Battlemage Ocato assures us that all the resources of the Elder Council, the Legions, the Guard, the Arcane University, and the Imperial Battle College are being employed to bring the assassins to justice. But, in the meantime, the greatest tribute we citizens can offer to the memory of our beloved Emperor is to go earnestly and diligently about our daily affairs, honoring the life of the great Empire he loved so much, and served so faithfully for so long.

[pagebreak]

泰姆瑞尔皇帝尤里尔·赛普汀七世驾崩，享年87岁，执掌帝国权柄逾六十五载。其遗体于水晶塔密室遭身份不明的暗杀者伏击。同日不同地点，故皇三位继承人（皇储盖尔多，56岁；恩曼亲王，55岁；艾伯尔亲王，53岁）亦遭神秘力量屠戮。元老议会、帝国近卫军及刃卫禁军已立案彻查此次弑君事件，惟三方机构严令禁止传播与此案相关的任何报道及流言，直至另行通告。 根据古老宪章，元老议会将在新皇加冕前摄政帝国。皇统嫡脉已绝嗣枝尽断，议会尚未议定储君人选。元老议会发言人、帝国战法师兼首席执政官奥卡托面向全境发布告谕，恳请子民保持克制，并在祷告时追思先皇、众皇子及议会元勋。 尤里尔七世治世前期以太平盛世著称。皇后考拉·沃莉娅为皇室诞下三位康健皇子，既是皇帝的贤内助，亦是深受爱戴的国民之母。然第三纪元389-399年的「帝国幻象时期」使帝国蒙受浩劫——皇帝遭囚于湮灭领域，僭主贾加尔·索恩以幻术窃据皇帝的长相以偷取政权。最终经巫女莉亚·西尔曼与其无名门徒的斡旋，真皇得以重掌权柄。然经此剧变，帝国纲纪废弛，心力交瘁的皇后亦从此退隐深宫。 复辟后的数十年间，泰姆瑞尔重归和平繁荣。然而西北诸邦日趋紧张的政治局势最终引爆了伊利亚克湾战争，这场冲突不仅确立了匕落城、哨城、途歇城与奥辛纽姆的现代疆界，更以引发「西部异变」的传奇事件收场。 帝权暮年，帝国的荣光普照诸省。宗教纷争与瓦登费尔危局得以安然化解，在赫尔斯王与巴兰兹亚女王睿智果决的治术引领下，帝国文明之辉穿越晨风省的重峦叠嶂，终至泽被边陲。 皇帝陛下与三位皇子遇刺，是动摇帝国的重大罪行，也是整个泰姆瑞尔最惨痛的悲剧。战法师奥卡托代表元老院向民众保证：帝国军团、都城守卫、奥秘大学和帝国战争学院已动用所有力量追查凶手。在此期间，我们作为公民对陛下最好的悼念，就是恪尽职守维持日常生活，以此传承他毕生挚爱并倾尽心血守护的伟大帝国精神。

original: What's the news from the other parts of Tamriel?
string: 泰姆瑞尔其他地区有什么消息？

original: Heard any news from the other provinces?
string: 有其他省份的消息吗？

original: Any news?
string: 有新消息吗？

original: What's the latest?
string: 最新消息是什么？

original: Heard any news lately?
string: 最近有什么新闻吗？

original: This is most disturbing. We can only hope this madness is over soon.
string: 这太令人不安了。我们只能希望这场疯狂尽快结束。

original: This is unbelievable. How can the gods let this happen?
string: 这简直难以置信。神怎么能让这种事发生？

original: It seems it is a dire situation throughout all of Tamriel.
string: 看来整个泰姆瑞尔的形势都很严峻。

original: I've been trying to get through "Mysterious Akavir." It's a fairly interesting read.
string: 我一直在读《神秘的阿卡维尔》，挺有意思的。

original: I've been reading "Fundaments of Alchemy." I figure it can't hurt to learn something new.
string: 我一直在读《炼金术基础》。我觉得学点新东西总归没坏处。

original: I've been reading "Overview of Gods and Worship." I'm not sure if I like it yet.
string: 我一直在读《诸神概览与信仰》。我还不确定自己是否喜欢这本书。

original: I read "The Real Barenziah" recently. Quite a piece of work.
string: 我最近读了《真正的巴兰兹亚》。真是一部佳作。

original: I've been trying to finish "Brief History of the Empire." It's a lot to take in.
string: 我一直在努力读完《帝国简史》。内容实在太多，有点难以消化。

original: A friend gave me "The Book of Daedra." It's an interesting study.
string: 一位朋友给了我一本《魔族之书》。这是一本有趣的读物。

original: I picked up "Frontier, Conquest." Haven't read much, though.
string: 我拿了本《前线，征服》。不过还没怎么读。

original: I'm finally getting around to reading "Five Songs of King Wulfharth." I just wish I had more time to read it.
string: 我终于开始读《武夫哈斯王的五首歌》了。只是希望我能有更多时间来读它。

original: I was given "The Legendary Scourge." I don't know what to think about it yet.
string: 我得到了《传奇的灾难》这本书。我还不知道该怎么评价它。

original: I've never read that. Been meaning to pick it up, though. Perhaps I can read it when you're finished.
string: 我从未读过那本书。一直想找个时间读一读。或许等你读完后我可以看看。

original: Ah... an excellent read, though it's been a while since I've read it myself. Let me know how you like it.
string: 啊......这是一本很好的读物，虽然我自己已经有一段时间没有读过了。你喜欢吗？

original: Hmm... not my favorite work, but many enjoy it.
string: 嗯......不是我最喜欢的作品，但很多人喜欢。

original: That sounds interesting. Perhaps I'll have to read it as well.
string: 听起来很有趣。也许我也要读一读。

original: I've not read that yet. It's a shame there isn't more time to spend with good books.
string: 我还没读过。可惜没有更多的时间来读好书。

original: I believe I read that some time ago. I'll have to give it another read.
string: 我想我前段时间读过这本书。我得再读一读。

original: They say Helgen got hit by a dragon.
string: 他们说海尔根被一条龙袭击了。

original: The Greybeards have summoned the Dragonborn to High Hrothgar. Such a thing has not happened for... hundreds of years.
string: 灰髯士召唤龙裔前去高吼修道院了。这种事已经……好几百年没发生过了。

original: There was a fight down in the Ratway, but reports are... sketchy. Some say it was Thalmor Agents, others say Thieves Guild. Some say it was both.
string: 在鼠道发生了一场斗殴，但是回报结果……十分含糊。有人说是梭默特使，另外一些人说是盗贼公会。还有说两者都有的。

original: Word is Elenwen's furious. Big party at the Thalmor Embassy, and one of the guests went someplace they shouldn't. Caused quite a commotion.
string: 据说爱琳温最近很暴躁。在梭默大使馆举行的盛大的聚会里，有一个客人进入了不该进的地方。这事造成了很大的骚动。

original: Have you heard? There's been another dragon attack. Kynesgrove, this time.
string: 你听说了吗？又有龙发动攻击。这次在凯娜之林。

original: The Greybeards have arranged a truce between the Stormcloaks and Imperials. How long can such a thing last?
string: 在灰髯士的斡旋下风暴斗篷和帝国之间达成了停战协定。这能维持多久？

original: The Greybeards have called a peace council, at High Hrothgar. And can you believe it - both Ulfric Stormcloak and General Tullius have agreed to go.
string: 灰髯士在高吼修道院安排了一个和平会议。而且你能相信吗——风氅氏的乌弗瑞克和图利乌斯将军居然都同意出席。

original: You hear the news? The Emperor has been murdered! Right here, in Skyrim. By the gods, if the Dark Brotherhood can do that, nobody's safe...
string: 你听说了吗？皇帝被杀了！就在这里，在天际。天啊，要是黑暗兄弟会能做到这种程度，那就没有他们杀不了的人了……

original: By the gods. The Emperor's been murdered. On his own ship... moored in the inlet. It was... the Dark Brotherhood. There was nothing we could do...
string: 天啊。皇帝被刺杀了。就在港湾里停泊着的……他自己的私人船只上。是……黑暗兄弟会做的。我们什么也做不了。

original: That old woman who runs the orphanage has been murdered.
string: 孤儿院那个老太婆被杀了。

original: Been a murder, over in Riften. Some old lady who runs an orphanage. Those poor children must be heartbroken.
string: 在裂谷城，发生了一起谋杀。被害者是经营孤儿院的一位年老女性。那些可怜的孩子们一定很伤心。

original: The Emperor's cousin has been killed. Right here in Solitude.
string: 皇帝的表亲遇刺了。就在独孤城。

original: The cousin of the Emperor was murdered! In Solitude, at her own wedding I hear.
string: 皇帝的表妹被谋杀了！听说是在独孤城的婚礼上。

original: There are some that say the Dark Brotherhood is back and stronger than ever. That they've made Dawnstar their home.
string: 有人说黑暗兄弟会卷土重来了，比以往更强。他们把晨星当成了新据点。

original: They're saying the Dark Brotherhood has been destroyed. Wiped off the face off Tamriel.
string: 传言说黑暗兄弟会被彻底铲除了。从塔姆瑞尔大陆上消失了。

original: Maybe you haven't heard, but the Thieves Guild is back.
string: 或许你还没听说——盗贼公会东山再起了。

original: The say the College has been snooping around Saarthal. Mages in a burial crypt. No good can come of that...
string: 他们说学院最近在萨瑟尔城周边有所动作。有法师在墓穴里活动。恐怕不会干出什么好事……

original: Some are saying the Psijic Monks have been seen in Skyrim. They're an ancient order. I had 'em figured for dead.
string: 传说最近赛伊克僧侣出现在天际各地。他们是一个古老的组织。我一直以为他们已经消失了。

original: You hear the news? Those damn mages blew up Winterhold! Guess it was just a matter of time...
string: 你还没有听说吗？那些该死的法师炸毁了冬堡！用猜的也知道不过是时间问题而已……

original: Word is the College of Mages is back to normal. If there's such a thing for that lot.
string: 听说法师学院已经恢复正常了。如果像他们一样的地方有很多就糟了。

original: As if Skyrim didn't have enough outsiders. Now we've got mercenaries from Hammerfell struttin' about...
string: 好像天际的异乡人还不够多似的。现在我们又有了来自落锤省的佣兵四处游荡……

original: Kodlak killed. Jorrvaskr attacked. How could this happen within the walls of Whiterun?
string: 科拉克被杀，月瓦斯卡遭袭。白漫城墙之内怎会发生这种事？

original: I hear the East Empire Company has reopened. All of Skyrim benefits from their trade.
string: 东帝国公司重新开张了。整个天际省的贸易都能沾光。

original: First Torygg and now Elisif. Damn those Stormcloaks. Let's hope that Erikur fares better than they did.
string: 先是托依格然后是艾利西弗。该死的风暴斗篷。希望艾瑞克尔不要步上他们的后尘。

original: Looks like it's really happening. A peace council, attended by both Ulfric and Tullius, up on High Hrothgar. Maybe there's hope for Skyrim yet.
string: 看来真的成功了。一个和平会谈，有乌弗瑞克和图利乌斯同时出席，在高吼修道院举行。说不定天际真的还有一线希望。

original: Thalmor in the Ratway? What's next, Spriggans in the Bee and Barb?
string: 鼠道里出现梭默？下一个是什么？蜂与钩里出现树精？

original: Helgen... destroyed by a dragon. Hard to believe, isn't it?
string: 赫迩镇……被一只龙摧毁了。难以置信，对吧？

original: The Emperor's cousin Vittoria Vici is getting married soon. The reception will be public - anyone in Solitude can attend.
string: 皇帝的表姐妹维多利亚·薇齐就快要结婚了。婚礼对大众开放——到时候只要是待在独孤城的人都可以参加。

original: One of the guards said he saw a mage appear out of thin air. Claimed it was one of those Psijic Monks. Man's been hitting the skooma, I say.
string: 有一个卫兵说看见一个法师凭空出现。据他说那是一个赛伊克僧侣。要我的说，这家伙肯定嗑了斯库玛。

original: They say that when you murder someone, the Dark Brotherhood comes to you in your sleep. It's how they recruit new members.
string: 传言说如果你杀了人，黑暗兄弟会会趁你睡觉时找上门。他们就这么招募新成员的。

original: I might swim more if it weren't for the slaughterfish. Sharp teeth, and some carry disease.
string: 要不是有食人鱼，我倒愿意多游游泳——牙尖嘴利，有些还带毒。

original: They say there's a cave north of Whiterun where the dead don't stay dead...
string: 据说白漫城北边有个洞穴，里面的死者不会安息……

original: Did you hear? A ghost ship was seen off the coast of Solitude. Vanished before anyone could get close.
string: 听说了吗？有人看见独孤城海岸外有艘幽灵船。还没等靠近就消失无踪了。

original: Something strange is happening with the moons. The mages in Winterhold are worried, but they won't say why.
string: 双月出异象。冬堡那群法师慌得很，可谁也不肯说缘由。

original: Some farmers near Rorikstead claim their livestock were drained dry. Vampires, maybe?
string: 罗瑞林德附近的农户说牲畜全被吸干了血。八成是吸血鬼干的？

original: The Jarl of Markarth is acting strange. He's holding closed-door meetings with unknown visitors.
string: 马卡斯城的领主举止古怪，总关着门和神秘访客密谈。

original: There's talk of a dragon priest stirring in an old tomb. Best keep away from ancient ruins, I say.
string: 传闻有龙祭司在古墓里苏醒。要我说，离那些遗迹远点儿为妙。

original: A child in Morthal hasn't spoken in weeks. Some say she's cursed. Others say she's a seer.
string: 莫萨尔有个孩子几周不说话了。有人说她中了咒，也有人称她是先知。

original: They say a man in Windhelm was cursed to live forever... but no one's seen him in years.
string: 听说风盔城有个人被诅咒永生……但好些年没人见过他了。

original: The miners in Shor's Stone dug too deep. Now they're hearing things at night.
string: 舒尔之石的矿工挖得太深，现在夜里总能听见怪声。

original: Fishermen in Dawnstar keep pulling up old Nord artifacts. Must be something under the ice.
string: 晨星城的渔夫总捞到诺德古物。冰层底下怕是有大东西。

original: They found a shrine to Namira in a cave near Falkreath. Whole place smelled like death.
string: 佛克瑞斯附近的洞穴里发现了娜米拉祭坛。整个洞窟弥漫着尸臭味。

original: An Argonian was dragged out of the river in Eastmarch - eyes wide open, but no breath in him. Looked like he drowned in pure fear.
string: 东境领河里捞上来个亚龙人——眼睛瞪得老大，却没了气息。活活被吓死的模样。

original: Children near Dawnstar are drawing symbols in the snow. No one taught them, and none of them remember doing it.
string: 晨星城的小孩在雪地上画神秘符号。没人教过，他们自己也不记得画过。

original: They say a hunter found a deer with silver blood. Melted his blade when he tried to carve it.
string: 听说猎人逮到只流银色血的鹿。用刀割肉时刀刃都熔化了。

original: Someone's been leaving black feathers on the Jarl's throne in Falkreath. No one's seen who... or what.
string: 佛克瑞斯领主的王座上总出现黑羽毛。没人瞧见是谁……或什么东西放的。

original: They say a Nord girl vanished during a storm and came back weeks later, eyes glowing blue. Says she 'spoke to Shor.'
string: 有个诺德姑娘在暴风雨中失踪，几周后回来时双眼泛蓝光。声称“与舒尔交谈过”。

original: A boy in Riverwood keeps drawing circles on the floor with ash. Claims he's keeping 'them' out. No one knows who 'they' are.
string: 河木镇男孩总用灰烬在地上画圈，说是要防“他们”进来。可谁都不知道“他们”是谁。

original: The College in Winterhold is hiding something. One of their apprentices exploded - twice - and no one's talking.
string: 冬堡学院藏着秘密。有个学徒炸了两次，结果所有人闭口不谈。

original: There's a tree near Kynesgrove that grows apples in the shape of faces. No one will eat them.
string: 凯娜之林附近长了棵怪树，结的苹果全像人脸。没人敢吃。

original: Fishermen near the Sea of Ghosts say the water sings some nights. Real low, like it's mourning something.
string: 亡灵海边的渔民说，某些夜晚海水会低吟，像在哀悼什么。

original: A black goat's been seen wandering the roads at night. Doesn't eat, doesn't blink. Just stares.
string: 有只黑山羊总在夜路上游荡。不吃不眨，只会死盯着人看。

original: A guard near Solitude said he caught a glimpse of a man without a shadow. He reported it - and disappeared the next day.
string: 独孤城守卫说他瞥见个没影子的人。刚上报完，次日自己就失踪了。

original: An old woman in the Reach was found with no eyes, but she'd sewn her mouth shut. Still alive. Still humming.
string: 边塞领发现个没眼珠的老太婆，自己用线缝死了嘴。还活着，还哼着曲儿。

original: A man in Riften found an old staff in a chest. Every time he touches it, he forgets the last three days.
string: 裂谷城有人从箱子里翻出根旧法杖，每摸一次就忘记前三天的事。

original: Have you heard? The Jesters College in Camlorn graduated another class.
string: 最新消息！卡姆伦的滑稽戏学院又毕业了一批小丑。

original: Red Mountain is still erupting. You can see it if you go to Solstheim.
string: 红山仍在喷发。去索瑟姆就能望见滚滚烟柱。

original: The Empire's falling apart at the seams. I heard bandits are running parts of Cyrodiil now, and even the Colovian nobles don't trust the Emperor.
string: 帝国正分崩离析。听说西罗帝尔的某些区域已被匪帮控制，连科洛维亚贵族都不再信任皇帝。

original: Many believe Cyrodiil is rife with political strife and warlords rising in the provinces. The Thalmor's influence is said to be choking the Imperial Court.
string: 都说西罗帝尔党争四起，各省军阀割据。而梭默的影响力正扼住帝国宫廷的咽喉。

original: The Redguards told the Thalmor to get out, and they meant it. I hear they're still fighting skirmishes on the border.
string: 红卫人把梭默轰了出去。边境至今仍有小规模冲突——他们可是动真格的。

original: Breton kings are always plotting. Some say they're preparing for war - maybe even against each other.
string: 布莱顿的国王们总在密谋。有人说他们在备战——说不定要内战。

original: They say the Thalmor are doing... strange things in Alinor. People vanish, and nobody asks questions.
string: 梭默在艾琳诺搞些……邪门勾当。活人凭空蒸发，却没任何人追问。

original: I heard the Green Pact is being twisted by the Thalmor. Whole villages wiped out for breaking sacred laws.
string: 听说绿约律法被梭默曲解。好几个村庄因触犯圣律遭到屠戮。

original: The Thalmor have a firm grip on Valenwood, and Bosmer loyal to the old ways may be rebelling in the forests. Some say the Wild Hunt may rise again if things get worse.
string: 梭默牢牢掌控着瓦伦森林，而坚守旧道的木精灵可能在密林反抗。若局势恶化，狂猎兽潮或将再现。

original: No one goes into Argonia anymore. They say the Hist are changing the Argonians into something... different.
string: 如今没人敢踏入黑沼泽。传言希斯特古树正把阿尔贡人改造成……异化之物。

original: Some whisper that the Hist are preparing for a new era - one where Argonia becomes the dominant power in Tamriel.
string: 私语说希斯特在筹备新纪元——届时阿尔贡人将主宰塔姆瑞尔。

original: Rumors from Morrowind tell of strange Daedric cults rising again in secret corners of the land, and of Telvanni mages rebuilding ancient towers.
string: 晨风省传来秘闻：隐秘角落滋生着诡异的迪德拉邪教，泰尔瓦尼法师正在重建古塔。

original: They say the Legion's got deserters patrolling the roads now. Can't tell if you're safer with 'em or without 'em.
string: 如今连帝国军团都派逃兵巡路。说不好遇上他们算不算安全。

original: Imperial City's still standing, but barely. Half the nobles are bought by the Thalmor, the other half are dead.
string: 帝都虽未陷落，却也摇摇欲坠。半数贵族被梭默收买，余下的坟头草已三丈高。

original: Redguards don't take orders from anyone - kicked the Dominion out on their arses. Now that's a people with backbone.
string: 红卫人只听自己的号令——用刀剑请走先祖神州。这才叫有骨气的民族！

original: The Alik'r talk of a 'silent war' in the sands. Border raids, assassins... wouldn't surprise me if Hammerfell's preparing for something big.
string: 阿里克尔沙漠流传着"无声战争"：边境突袭、暗杀行动……若说落锤在谋划大动作，我绝不意外。

original: Some say the Direnni are stirring again. No proof, but... old names have power, you know?
string: 有人称迪仁尼家族正悄然复苏。虽无实据……但古老姓氏的余威，你懂吧？

original: Bosmer don't like outsiders anymore. Friend of mine went looking for rare game - came back missing a hand.
string: 木精灵不再待见外人。我有个朋友去猎珍兽——回来时少了只手。

original: Heard the Green Pact's gone mad. A village was burned for planting flowers. Flowers!
string: 绿约律法疯了！听说有个村子因种花被焚毁——种花啊！

original: We've got our freedom, but it didn't come cheap. My brother still fights in the Alik'r deserts.
string: 自由代价惨重。我哥还在阿里克尔沙漠征战。

original: The Crowns and Forebears nearly came to civil war again last season. Hammerfell's wounds are deep, even without the Dominion's blade.
string: 拥王派与先祖蛾教团上季度几乎内战重燃。即便没有梭默，落锤的旧伤依然溃烂。

original: Saw ships fly banners I've never seen. Strange glyphs. Mages in High Rock have started their own kingdom, I wager.
string: 见过挂着诡异纹章的船队。八成是高岩法师自立了王国。

original: Something's wrong in the Isles. Even the sun feels different there now... like it's watching you.
string: 夏暮群岛不对劲。连阳光都阴恻恻的……像在监视你。

original: The Dominion's building a road straight through the jungle. Chopped down half a grove - next day, every worker was dead. No wounds. Just... gone.
string: 先祖神州的穿林大道工程砍伐了半片圣林——次日所有劳工暴毙。无伤无痕……就这么断了气。

original: I heard there's a plague in the Tenmar Forest. Or maybe a rebellion. Hard to say - Khajiit don't talk much about what's really going on.
string: 听说坦玛尔森林闹瘟疫——也可能是起义。虎人从不多谈真实动向。

original: Hist sap's changing. More potent. Dangerous, even. A few Argonian students drank it - woke up days later speaking languages no one knew.
string: 希斯特树液愈发浓烈，甚至带毒。几个亚龙人学生误饮后，醒来竟说着无人知晓的古老语言。

original: Black Marsh is growing. Literally. Swamps swallowing villages near the border. Bet the trees'll reach Cyrodiil in a few years.
string: 黑沼泽在蔓延——字面意义。边境村庄正被沼泽吞噬，不出五年能吞到西罗帝尔。

original: They found an entire village outside Daggerfall... sleeping. No wounds, no signs of struggle. Just asleep. And none of them will wake up.
string: 达格斯城外发现整座沉睡村庄。无伤无争——就是叫不醒。

original: Heard the Empire's crumbling faster than a draugr's tomb. They say the Imperial City's still scarred from the Great War, and the nobles bicker while bandits rule the roads.
string: 听说帝国崩塌得比尸鬼墓穴还快。帝都仍残留大战伤疤，贵族扯皮时匪徒已占山为王。

original: A traveler from Cyrodiil came through last week. Said the Thalmor are strutting about the Imperial City like they own it. Makes my blood boil!
string: 上周有个西罗帝尔旅人说梭默在帝都横行霸道。听得我红温了！

original: They say High Rock's wizards are meddling with things best left alone. Some fool mage opened a gate to Oblivion, or so the caravans claim.
string: 高岩巫师总摆弄禁忌之物。商队传言有个蠢货法师打开了湮灭之门。

original: Some Redguard sailors washed up in Dawnstar, muttering about sea monsters off the coast of Hammerfell. Probably just drank too much rum, if you ask me.
string: 几个红卫水手漂到晨星城，念叨着落锤海岸有海怪。要我说准是朗姆酒喝多了。

original: They say Hammerfell's deserts are crawling with bandits now that the Empire's gone. Good. Let the Redguards handle their own mess.
string: 自帝国撤军后，落锤沙漠匪帮横行。挺好——红卫人的烂摊子自己收拾。

original: Heard the Argonians are brewing poisons that can kill a man with a single drop. Probably selling 'em to the Thalmor, the sneaky lizards.
string: 亚龙人在炼一滴毙命的奇毒。八成卖给梭默——那些狡猾的蜥蜴。

original: Heard the High Elves are building ships to invade Tamriel again. Mark my words, they won't stop 'til we're all bowing to their so-called 'superiority.'
string: 高等精灵在造舰准备再侵塔姆瑞尔。记住我的话：他们不逼所有人跪拜"优越种族"誓不罢休！

original: Some crazy fool in Whiterun's claiming they're the Dragonborn, shouting at the sky like a lunatic. Probably just drank too much mead.
string: 白漫城有个疯子自称龙裔，整天对天吼叫。八成是蜜酒灌多了。

original: Dawnstar's cursed, I swear. Nightmares plague the folk there, and some say it's Daedra work from that old museum.
string: 晨星城绝对遭了诅咒！镇上的人夜夜噩梦，都说是那旧博物馆里的迪德拉作祟。

original: Those mages at the College of Winterhold are meddling with forbidden magic. No wonder the Nords don't trust 'em.
string: 冬堡学院的法师在鼓捣禁忌魔法。难怪诺德人不待见他们。

original: A hunter from Falkreath swore he saw a ghost in the woods, glowing pale and muttering about betrayal. Probably just the fog playing tricks.
string: 佛克瑞斯的猎人赌咒说林子里有苍白的鬼影，念叨着背叛。大概是大雾迷了眼。

original: They say Maven Black-Briar's got a deal with a Daedric Prince. How else does she keep Riften under her thumb?
string: 都说玛雯·黑荆棘和迪德拉王子做了交易。不然她哪能把裂谷城捏得死死的？

original: Thalmor agents were seen snooping around Falkreath's graveyard. Probably looking for Talos worshippers to drag off.
string: 梭默特工在佛克瑞斯墓地转悠。准是来抓塔洛斯信徒的。

original: Heard Whiterun's mead supply ran dry last week. The whole city panicked - folk were trying to brew ale from cabbages!
string: 听说白漫城的蜜酒上周断供了！全城都疯了——有人甚至试图用卷心菜酿麦酒！

original: Folk in Morthal swear the marsh is haunted by a ghost who keeps stealing their boots. Only the left ones, mind you.
string: 莫萨尔居民发誓沼泽有专偷左靴的鬼魂。只偷左脚，绝不拿错。

original: They say a dragon landed in Ivarstead and demanded a tribute of sweetrolls. Ate a whole cart and flew off burping flames!
string: 传言有条龙降在伊瓦斯泰德，索要甜卷当贡品。吃完整辆推车，打着火嗝飞走了！

original: Heard a draugr in a barrow near Rorikstead keeps waking up to sweep the floors. Tidiest tomb in Skyrim, that one.
string: 听说洛里斯泰德附近的古坟里有尸鬼定期醒來扫地。那恐怕是天际最整洁的墓穴。

original: Heard the Thieves Guild stole Maven Black-Briar's favorite goblet, then sold it back to her for a hundred septims. She's still fuming!
string: 盗贼公会偷了玛雯·黑荆棘最爱的酒杯，又以一百金币卖还给她。她现在还在跳脚呢！

original: They say a skeever in Markarth's learned to pick locks. Keeps sneaking into the Silver-Bloods' treasury for snacks.
string: 马卡斯城有只耗子学会开锁，专溜进银血家族金库偷零食。

string: 听说马卡斯领主甜卷吃太多卡在王座里，三个守卫才把他撬出来
